<div class="toc-heading">Nuclear Notebook</div>
<h1><span class="NLM_article-title hlFld-title">North Korean nuclear capabilities, 2018</span></h1><div class="literatumAuthors"><div class="publicationContentAuthors"><div class="hlFld-ContribAuthor"><span class="NLM_contrib-group"><span class="contribDegrees corresponding "><div class="entryAuthor"><a class="author" href="/author/Kristensen%2C+Hans+M">Hans M. Kristensen<i class="fa fa-envelope" aria-hidden="true" style="margin-left: 0.5em;"></i></a><span class="overlay"><span class="corr-sec"><span class="heading">Correspondence</span><span class="corr-email"><i class="fa fa-envelope" style="color: #10147E; padding-right: 7px" aria-hidden="true"></i><a href="mailto:hkristensen@fas.org rnorris@fas.org">hkristensen@fas.org rnorris@fas.org</a></span><br /></span><a class="author-extra-info hasFull" href="#B0001">View further author information</a></span></div> &amp; </span><span class="contribDegrees "><div class="entryAuthor"><a class="author" href="/author/Norris%2C+Robert+S">Robert S. Norris</a><span class="overlay"><a class="author-extra-info hasFull" href="#B0002">View further author information</a></span></div></span></span></div></div></div></div>
</div>
</div>
